get_openapi_url
================

.. autofunction:: get_openapi_url

Gets the OpenAPI URL for a plugin.

Parameters
----------
url : str
    The URL of the plugin.

Returns
-------
str
    The OpenAPI URL for the plugin.

Purpose
-------
This function is used to retrieve the OpenAPI URL for a plugin given its URL. The OpenAPI URL points to the OpenAPI spec which describes the endpoints, parameters and responses of the API.


